tid":777671,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5192833a6f613eb39eb12109e26284d79086216","tid":777671,"uid":70183,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"試過入梗機場開始著燈<br />\n<br />\n回程出左機場上左公路先記得未入<br />\n<br />\n渣到番屯門係青公加德士入<br />\n<br />\n接機坐左四個人四個大喼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b565eacecaa811c495ea1e90011e6286723b0cdf","tid":777671,"uid":39907,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:58:25.000Z","msg":"通常1/4, 舊車下下到底電油泵好快收皮"},{"pid":"e5947a3b267d7e05e94e374d17c24adc6a4ecc11","tid":777671,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c3362ea0cdd75c5b82ed76923cffb6a13a28191","tid":777671,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5192833a6f613eb39eb12109e26284d79086216","tid":777671,"uid":70183,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"試過入梗機場開始著燈<br />\n<br />\n回程出左機場上左公路先記得未入<br />\n<br />\n渣到番屯門係青公加德士入<br />\n<br />\n接機坐左四個人四個大喼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:09:48.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14aca46ed2fdb86cf5b3f354a6488d85a66232d7","tid":777671,"uid":195215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:11:32.000Z","msg":"岩岩4格去入滿vpower<br />\n上一缸油應該係普通油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f6a884ce51b3c06cadb171a06b46def8dc8c65","tid":777671,"uid":48623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:17:41.000Z","msg":"傳聞著油燈都行到幾十公里，試過有次係停車場一著車即著油燈。但因為趕時間就唯有死頂熄曬冷氣收音機，深井出旺角接人再返荃灣先入油。睇住支油針由兩格變一格再變返兩格，嚇到袋低都濕埋。<br />\n另外大家覺唔覺油針熱車時會顯示多小小？咁我應該睇熱車時既油針定一著車個油針為準？"},{"pid":"84613ce3135cbecec198d15fa0dcb68c0d55ff66","tid":777671,"uid":50417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:33:59.000Z","msg":"可以問返廠，着油燈時太概剩番幾多升油，咁你就心裏有數。如果答你起碼行到50km呢啲答案可以無視。"},{"pid":"9b4992bd3808a858e8379e6a09c0e2f5362b68f8","tid":777671,"uid":44897,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"見過有岸鳩仔離油站300米冇晒油，要用鐵鑵買油入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54a1c2a295213c47d9d899c3ef0bbc7fbc76a93","tid":777671,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b4992bd3808a858e8379e6a09c0e2f5362b68f8","tid":777671,"uid":44897,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"見過有岸鳩仔離油站300米冇晒油，要用鐵鑵買油入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:05:42.000Z","msg":"好似要登記, 係咪呀?"},{"pid":"66061bdf3ad901069267508b8c0971cd3af0cc9a","tid":777671,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e54a1c2a295213c47d9d899c3ef0bbc7fbc76a93","tid":777671,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b4992bd3808a858e8379e6a09c0e2f5362b68f8","tid":777671,"uid":44897,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"見過有岸鳩仔離油站300米冇晒油，要用鐵鑵買油入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:05:42.000Z","msg":"好似要登記, 係咪呀?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:24:10.000Z","msg":"我係見到佢倒返油入車，唔知有冇登記<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前睇過介紹好似就唔洗登記，不過只可以買3/5L"},{"pid":"1b813a2ca390af35387177c6584e3ddebef5ea79","tid":777671,"uid":16710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:29:06.000Z","msg":"淨5小格就入，成日到底油泵好快玩完"},{"pid":"29fe92c839141b6e940793ec4ba638e17371690f","tid":777671,"uid":18948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/13/173018_c6b240028e33b02ad7d816ee9213fd5f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2F173018_c6b240028e33b02ad7d816ee9213fd5f.png&h=de252f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n油站影的"},{"pid":"810907f0ac29587671c22b1eb6b159254316940f","tid":777671,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29fe92c839141b6e940793ec4ba638e17371690f","tid":777671,"uid":18948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/13/173018_c6b240028e33b02ad7d816ee9213fd5f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2F173018_c6b240028e33b02ad7d816ee9213fd5f.png&h=de252f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n油站影的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:31:49.000Z","msg":"果次0咗之後起碼行多咗5公里都未死"},{"pid":"2c0a016e84e6267a79dd0d49dbc334645dc34a22","tid":777671,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:49:19.000Z","msg":"著燈就入"},{"pid":"dbc247a82650392444197ebd639cf05a49f39792","tid":777671,"uid":71768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"732c2d1b0d38a564e43e1488da47b6f87e3e3fae","tid":777671,"uid":174882,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"14ee21dc92630e506a4503c13a1f2428bb1ff5bb","tid":777671,"uid":71768,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T06:09:06.000Z","msg":"用到著燈先入 或者指到最低又未著燈（會走遠程時會咁做）通常用到底"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T06:23:22.000Z","msg":"香港就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他地方要去到有火星先有油站嘅<br />\n你睇map同油耗要計劃下踩幾深同第幾個油站要入"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:55:11.000Z","msg":"唔係問香港咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來外國處境題 sorry囉"},{"pid":"0b67a2e906bd59e0b9475d5ddbc614ba901413e3","tid":777671,"uid":41803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T10:20:26.000Z","msg":"次次到著燈用加德士400蚊劵"},{"pid":"d7e9adbf2a5306ad8e5c9d80c4b848231c9f4f21","tid":777671,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68da465ac2ba38ca50fa9ef691f9b6e355c30a15","tid":777671,"uid":197869,"like":2,"dislike":46,"score":-44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T06:11:24.000Z","msg":"用盡先好入呀，溝油好傷車架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T10:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0e65230776e582521798251f2e00bb8baf4aa7","tid":777671,"uid":19560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:38:38.000Z","msg":"部車提我入咪入 (通常得返5L / 50KM RANGE)"},{"pid":"ed201b15599997de2e4239e90da5635d27792148","tid":777671,"uid":19560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a0e65230776e582521798251f2e00bb8baf4aa7","tid":777671,"uid":19560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:38:38.000Z","msg":"部車提我入咪入 (通常得返5L / 50KM RANGE)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:40:07.000Z","msg":"70Liter 油缸 入滿重到hihi, 通常入45L / $700 算 夠用成個星期"},{"pid":"816487b0440825f2cffa402302df1d8f0df1efa0","tid":777671,"uid":19560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29fe92c839141b6e940793ec4ba638e17371690f","tid":777671,"uid":18948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/13/173018_c6b240028e33b02ad7d816ee9213fd5f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2F173018_c6b240028e33b02ad7d816ee9213fd5f.png&h=de252f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n油站影的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:41:19.000Z","msg":"我都試過range得返單位數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾驚要推車入油站... 冷氣都關L埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44debed84945b610bf4bce37215ba8a34a12ac1a","tid":777671,"uid":43833,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"其實底油行到幾多係有數得計<br />\n<br />\n首先你要知自己油缸有幾大，以我為例係41L<br />\n<br />\n之後你要知用左幾多油先會著油燈，我次次如果一著油燈就去入油，叫彈槍的話都係入31-33L油。咁減返我油缸容量，即係有大概10L底油。<br />\n<br />\n而家10L油大概170蚊，扣埋折扣就大約14x左右。你再計自己部車行幾錢一公里，我就大概行0.9-1.4一公里，我當大數1.4，即係我著油燈應該行到100公里。然後保險起見我再打個八折，行80公里應該係無問題<br />\n<br />\n其他車都可以咁計，以我經驗，大部份車著油燈都會有10L底油，你根據自己油耗去計就可以知道大概"},{"pid":"99ded372be959966f012bfc8d4f7b150127e7604","tid":777671,"uid":79410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:57:39.000Z","msg":"無定. 總之每逢星期二,三入. <br />\n楂返工,一星期啱啱好用一缸油"},{"pid":"3c23712b5696259b7090ca982a6f95b4e56b76dd","tid":777671,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"810907f0ac29587671c22b1eb6b159254316940f","tid":777671,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29fe92c839141b6e940793ec4ba638e17371690f","tid":777671,"uid":18948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/13/173018_c6b240028e33b02ad7d816ee9213fd5f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2F173018_c6b240028e33b02ad7d816ee9213fd5f.png&h=de252f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n油站影的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:31:49.000Z","msg":"果次0咗之後起碼行多咗5公里都未死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:58:35.000Z","msg":"佢嚇你叫你快啲搵油站啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n架架車都係咁  油量0或者km0<br />\n低油耗仲可以捱到10k~20k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢事你冇力推車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b837a02b7de122d35b6ed25b69a474133cfbd39","tid":777671,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44debed84945b610bf4bce37215ba8a34a12ac1a","tid":